{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be corporate and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sterling & Stone Legal</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #8b0000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #d3d3d3; /* Light Grey */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-footer-bg: #f8f8f8;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .intro {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n\n        .intro p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #6c0000; /* Darker red */\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Sterling & Stone Legal</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"intro\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>Dedicated to providing exceptional legal counsel and achieving favorable outcomes for our clients with integrity and expertise.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Practice Areas</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Guidance on mergers, acquisitions, compliance, and general corporate governance.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Litigation</h3>\n                    <p>Aggressive representation in civil and commercial disputes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Real Estate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Expertise in property transactions, zoning, and land use issues.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Intellectual Property</h3>\n                    <p>Protecting your patents, trademarks, and copyrights.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Sterling & Stone</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n                Founded on principles of justice and professional excellence, Sterling & Stone Legal has a long-standing reputation for delivering strategic, results-oriented legal services. Our team of experienced attorneys is committed to understanding your unique needs and providing tailored legal solutions. We pride ourselves on our deep industry knowledge and our unwavering dedication to our clients' success.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"6\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Sterling & Stone Legal. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic form submission simulation\n        document.querySelector('.contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch shortly.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}